3.1 Algorithm (Plain English)

The alarm will sound (Output = 0) ONLY if the Ignition is ON (IGN=1) AND (at least one of these two conditions is met):

    The Driver seat is occupied (DRIV=1) AND the Driver seatbelt is unfastened (BELTD=0).

    The Passenger seat is occupied (PASS=1) AND the Passenger seatbelt is unfastened (BELTP=0).
